-- Brazil Details Rules on Derivative Tax Exemptions for Exporters
-- B y   A n d r e   S o l i a n i
-- 2012-05-23T13:20:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-23/brazil-details-rules-on-derivative-tax-exemptions-for-exporters.html
Brazil’s tax agency published today
on the official gazette details on March 16 decision to exempt
exporters from a tax on currency derivatives.  The  Finance Ministry  didn’t immediately respond to
Bloomberg phone calls requesting details on the change.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andre Soliani in Brasilia at 
